This is a placeholder for the demo video.

To create the demo MP4:

1. Run the demo example:
   npm run dev:demo

2. Screen-record the browser window while navigating through all 7 segments
   (arrow keys to advance). Aim for 1920x1080.

3. Save the recording as docs/demo.mp4

4. Update README.md to embed the video (uncomment the video embed section
   near the "What it looks like" heading).

5. Delete this placeholder file.
